        "model": "tldr@v2.0.0",
        "text": "STREAMS is a batch and streaming platform which integrates and manages AI services for rich transcription, translation, voice synthesis and audio description, offering a rich array of multilingual services with innovative methods to enhance portability, responsiveness and output readability."
